page.title: 15SQUASH,COTEHILL
page.content: My favourite sport is squash .I am very keen on the game .I play at Carlisle squash rackets club which is next to the rugby pitch and the rugby club bar . Right next to that is Brunton Park, the football ground. I get coached by a professional squash player called Ronny Bell . I have a racket that cost Â£37. It is called a Dunlop Maxpli but most people use the new carbon fibre one's. They cost Â£50_55 . The squash club has 8 courts. Courts 7 and 8 are surrounded by a stadium where finals are played. I will soon enter the junior league and then start entering the competitions and hopefully by the age of 12_13 I will play for the county. My greatest ambition is to be the world's number 1 but I can't see much of that happening.
